Simulation -- This is Android App Developed On Android Studio Which helps us to understand:

	      1) Using Bluetooth Service to List all the available Users.

	      2) Splash Screen with animation at the beginning.

	      3) One time Registration Screen, Sign up Page is show only first time the app starts.

	      4) Uses of card view to display whatsapp like profile of user.

link to download the .apk file of the app:

